Paper: hep-th/9909213

Date: 1999-09-29

Title: On The Size of The Graviton

Authors: Nikita A. Nekrasov

Comments: 12pp. harvmac big mode, v3. refs, title and preprint number changed

We propose an approximate wavefunction of the bound state of $N$ $D0$-branes.Its spread grows as $N^{1\over 3}$ per particle, i.e. it saturates thePolchinski's bound.